<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<title>css选择符</title>
<style>
input:focus{color:#6F0; background:#9CF;border:1px solid red;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>四、伪类选择符 Pseudo-Classes Selectors</h1>
<div>5、E:focus--设置对象在成为输入焦点（该对象的onfocus事件发生）时的样式(IE6,7不支持)webkit内核浏览器会默认给:focus状态的元素加上outline的样式。</div>
<ul>
  <li>1111</li>
  <li><input type="text" value="111"></li>
  <li>111</li>
</ul>
<ul>
  <li>222</li>
  <li><input type="text" value="222"></li>
  <li>222</li>
</ul>
<ul>
  <li>333</li>
  <li>333</li>
  <li>333</li>
</ul>
</body>
</html>
